SELECT
  id,
  c_ticketid as ticket_id,
  dateCreated,
  c_owner AS owner,
  c_changeby AS change_by,
  c_memo AS memo,
  c_changedate AS change_date,
  c_ownergroup AS owner_group,
  c_assignedownergroup AS assignedownergroup,
  c_orgid AS org_id,
  c_statustracking AS statustracking,
  c_siteid AS site_ud,
  c_class AS class,
  c_ticketid AS ticket_id,
  c_status AS status,
  c_tkstatusid AS tkstatus_id,
  c_statustracking as statustracking
FROM app_fd_ticketstatus
WHERE c_ticketid = '#form.ticket.id#'
ORDER BY dateCreated DESC
